Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:41.803 --> 00:00:45.941
Shampure Shampoo is suitable for daily
hair shampooing.

00:00:46.103 --> 00:00:51.726
In this example, we use it for curls
because it cleans the hair gently and

00:00:51.888 --> 00:00:54.080
gives it a soothing aroma.

00:01:24.975 --> 00:01:29.443
Treat the clean hair with Shampure
conditioner.

00:01:29.605 --> 00:01:36.800
To avoid unnecessary stress to the hair,
apply only to lengths and tips.

00:01:46.378 --> 00:01:49.620
After 2-3 minutes, rinse the hair
thoroughly.

00:01:49.783 --> 00:01:54.890
The Mokikue protein formula protects the
hair from dangerous environmental

00:01:55.051 --> 00:01:57.760
influences and has a calming effect.

